			 general</header>
        <text>
          <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:530/ss:b/p:1">Paragraph (1) of section 530(b) of the Internal Revenue
