			 (4)(A)(ii)</cato:entity-ref> (as redesignated by <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="401Kids Family Savings Act of 2013/s:3/ss:b" proposed="true">subsection (b)</cato:entity-ref>) of section 530(b) of the
			 Internal Revenue Code of 1986 is amended by striking <quote>as defined in
			 paragraph (3)</quote> and inserting <quote>as defined in paragraph
			 (5)</quote>.</text>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="id7EADDCDF31914ED18E2ACA803113AA70">
